nodes.text: Clone Strike was the second set released for Wizards of the Coast's Star Wars Miniatures game. Released on December 13, 2004, it featured 60 figures from the prequel trilogy era. As with its predecessor, Rebel Storm, miniatures could be purchased in a booster pack of 7 random minis, or in a starter set, containing 8 random minis, as well as General Kenobi and Jango Fett, an updated rulebook, and a map (Muunilinst).
Rarity denoted as follows: Common (C), Uncommon (U), Rare (R), Very Rare (VR)
On March 16, 2005, Wizards released Ultimate Missions: Clone Strike, a book featuring 36 scenarios based on Clone Strike characters, as well as two maps (Coruscant and Geonosis) and map tiles.
